OL,3,CWoman jailed after attacking couple
OL,4,Cwith shovel and poker
OL,6,FA woman who assaulted a couple with a
OL,7,Fshovel and a poker has been sentenced
OL,8,Fto more than six years in prison.
OL,10,FPaula Attwood-Rees, from Usk,
OL,11,Fassaulted the man and woman, known to
OL,12,Fher, both outside and inside their
OL,13,Fhome in Monkswood in May this year.
OL,15,FThe 59-year-old entered the couple's
OL,16,Fhome where she punched the woman in
OL,17,Fthe face and hit the man on the head
OL,18,Fwith a poker.
