OL,6,FOutside of the property, she then hit
OL,7,Fthe woman with a shovel after causing
OL,8,Fdamage to two parked cars before being
OL,9,Fseparated and restrained by a passerby
OL,10,Fbefore officers arrived.
OL,12,FAttwood-Rees pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fwounding with intent, assault
OL,14,Foccasioning actual bodily harm,
OL,15,Faggravated burglary with intent,
OL,16,Fcommon assault of an emergency worker,
OL,17,Fand two counts of causing criminal
OL,18,Fdamage to property.
