OL,6,F"It was truly terrifying for these two
OL,7,Fvictims when the defendant burst into
OL,8,Ftheir home uninvited with the sole
OL,9,Fintention of attacking them and
OL,10,Fcausing harm.
OL,12,F"Luckily neither were seriously
OL,13,Finjured but the potential risk of harm
OL,14,Fthat these dangerous and prohibited
OL,15,Fweapons could have caused is
